<milestone unit="sentence" n="34" /> At <time value="4:15oclock">fifteen minutes past four o'clock</time>, the <rs>President</rs> (<persName n="Montague,Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00146" reg="nearbymention:Montague,E.,B.,," authname="montague,e.,b."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Montague</surname></persName> in the chair) announced the result of the vote, and declared the passage of the ordinance. </p> 
