<milestone unit="sentence" n="1018" />Engineer troops,<lb /><hi rend="smallcaps"><placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 5" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>,</hi> <date value="1861-06-17" authname="1861-06-17">June 17, 1861.</date></head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1019" /> <hi rend="bold">The undersigned having been duly</hi> authorized to enrol a corps of Sappees and Miners in the <placeName reg="Virginia" key="tgn,7007919" authname="tgn,7007919">State of Virginia</placeName>, for the <rs>Wise Brigade</rs>, has opened an office of envolment at the <rs type="place">Central Hotel building</rs>, corner of <address><street n="9 Street">9th</street></address> and <address><street n="Grac Street">Grac streets</street></address>, where the requirements of the service will be made known to those wishing to volunteer.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1020" />The especial attention of <persName n="Stone,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00684" reg="nearbymention:Stone,E.,W.,," authname="stone,e.,w."><surname full="yes">Stone</surname></persName> and Bric Masons, Blacksmiths, Wagon Makers, Bridge Builders, Miners, Quarrymen, etc., is particularly invited. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Donnellan,,G.,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00685" reg="default:Donnellan,G.,,," authname="donnellan,g."><foreName full="yes">G.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Donnellan</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> je <num value="17">17</num>--2t* <signed><rs type="role2">Captain</rs></signed> </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><orgName n="Jefferson Guard" type="guard">Jefferson Guard</orgName>, attention.</head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1021" /> A full meeting of this company is requested of their REndezvous, on <num value="20" type="ordinal">20th</num>, between <address><street n="Main street">Main</street></address> and <address><street n="Franklin street">Franklin streets</street></address>, at <time value="6oclock">6 o'clock</time> on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Monday</day></dateStruct> <time>evening</time> the <dateStruct value="--17" full="yes" authname="---17"><day reg="17" full="yes">17th inst.</day></dateStruct> This company is still open for Recruits.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1022" />All persons who are disposed to become members, will please attend at that time. </p> <closer> By order of <persName n="Moncure,Captain,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00686" reg="mostcommon:Moncure,nomatch:0" authname="moncure"><roleName n="Captain" full="yes">Capt.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Moncure</surname></persName>. je <num value="17">17</num>--1t* <signed><persName n="Moore,,James,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00687" reg="default:Moore,James,,," authname="moore,james"><foreName n="James" full="yes">Jas.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Moore</surname></persName>, O. S.</signed> </closer> </div3> </div2> 
